import React from 'react';
import Login from './Login';
import { AppRoute } from './AppRoute'
import StatiquePage from './StatiquePage';
import FamilleArticles from './FamilleArticles'
import AjoutFamilleArticles from './AjoutFamilleArticles'
import ModifFamilleArticles from './ModifFamilleArticles'
import Articles from './Articles'
import AjoutArticle from './AjoutArticle'
import ModifArticle from './ModifArticle'
import ExplArticle from './ExplArticle'
import Roles from './Roles'
import AjoutRole from './AjoutRole'
import ModifRole from './ModifRole'
import Utilisateurs from './Utilisateurs'
import AjoutUtilisateur from './AjoutUtilisateur'
import ModifUtilisateur from './ModifUtilisateur'
import Permissions from './Permissions'
import Unites from './Unites'
import AjoutUnite from './AjoutUnite'
import ModifUnite from './ModifUnite'
import Emplacements from './Emplacements'
import AjoutEmplacement from './AjoutEmplacement'
import ModifEmplacement from './ModifEmplacement'
import Inventaires from './Inventaires'
import { Link, BrowserRouter as Router, Route, Switch, withRouter } from 'react-router-dom'

function App() {
  return (
    <Router>
      <Switch>
        <AppRoute path="/ModifFamilleArticles" component={ModifFamilleArticles} layout={StatiquePage}></AppRoute>
        <AppRoute path="/AjoutFamilleArticles" component={AjoutFamilleArticles} layout={StatiquePage}></AppRoute>
        <AppRoute path="/ModifUtilisateur" component={ModifUtilisateur} layout={StatiquePage}></AppRoute>
        <AppRoute path="/AjoutUtilisateur" component={AjoutUtilisateur} layout={StatiquePage}></AppRoute>
        <AppRoute path="/AjoutEmplacement" component={AjoutEmplacement} layout={StatiquePage}></AppRoute>
        <AppRoute path="/ModifEmplacement" component={ModifEmplacement} layout={StatiquePage}></AppRoute>
        <AppRoute path="/FamilleArticles" component={FamilleArticles} layout={StatiquePage}></AppRoute>
        <AppRoute path="/ModifArticle" component={ModifArticle} layout={StatiquePage}></AppRoute>
        <AppRoute path="/AjoutArticle" component={AjoutArticle} layout={StatiquePage}></AppRoute>
        <AppRoute path="/Utilisateurs" component={Utilisateurs} layout={StatiquePage}></AppRoute>
        <AppRoute path="/Emplacements" component={Emplacements} layout={StatiquePage}></AppRoute>
        <AppRoute path="/ExplArticle" component={ExplArticle} layout={StatiquePage}></AppRoute>
        <AppRoute path="/Permissions" component={Permissions} layout={StatiquePage}></AppRoute>
        <AppRoute path="/Inventaires" component={Inventaires} layout={StatiquePage}></AppRoute>
        <AppRoute path="/ModifUnite" component={ModifUnite} layout={StatiquePage}></AppRoute>
        <AppRoute path="/AjoutUnite" component={AjoutUnite} layout={StatiquePage}></AppRoute>
        <AppRoute path="/ModifRole" component={ModifRole} layout={StatiquePage}></AppRoute>
        <AppRoute path="/AjoutRole" component={AjoutRole} layout={StatiquePage}></AppRoute>
        <AppRoute path="/Articles" component={Articles} layout={StatiquePage}></AppRoute>
        <AppRoute path="/Unites" component={Unites} layout={StatiquePage}></AppRoute>
        <AppRoute path="/Roles" component={Roles} layout={StatiquePage}></AppRoute>
        <Route path="/" render={() => <Login />} />
      </Switch>
    </Router>
  );
}

export default App;
